75
00:05:11.480 --> 00:05:11.960
efforts.

76
00:05:12.940 --> 00:05:16.290
So what does this mean for New Zealand's future productivity and

77
00:05:16.400 --> 00:05:20.360
contribution to the workforce? Firstly, quite simply,

78
00:05:20.780 --> 00:05:24.720
